Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: In the money
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xsz2
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 10 May 1987
From horse racing through gold and tennis to making movies, the big money continues to grow and grow. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less